Title: Not Everything's About Annalise
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Abby Ajayi, Erika Harrison (executive story editor), Fernanda Coppel (story editor), Morenike Balogun (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: As Annalise struggles to cope with prison life, Frank attempts to confess to Wes' murder with opposition from the DA. While the Keating 4 struggle over Annalise's innocence.
